snippet.textDisplay: Isn't it clear? If the origin was from a marketplace why would China be covering things up about the origin? Why would you pressure economicly countries that ask the question about the origin? If it did come from a market why would you do this, if you don't have something to hide you don't do this. It just is likely that this was an accident in the laboratory since it originated in Wuhan the place where we have a research on this virus. If it was an accident it would make sense that China acts in this way. We need to know and the problem is that China just isn't transparent this is the real issue what you should discus.
